text.tspan: Israel: New hospitalizations for moderate or severe
Shown is the rolling weekly sum of hospitalizations for moderate to severe COVID-19. Data is available at the
national level, plus breakdown by regions where vaccination began early or late.
Vaccination in Israel began on December 19 2020. Israel imposed a third national lockdown on January 8 2021.
